short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Reveal hidden Qualities in Fallen London storylets

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows you to see changes in the player qualities which are marked as "hidden" by the Fallen London API. Mostly of interest to data miners and Fallen London Wiki contributors.
